text: Käthe Lettner (born 13 December 1906, date of death unknown) was an Austrian alpine skier. She competed in the women's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1906 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Austrian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Austria Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from Bad Ischl Category:Sportspeople from Upper Austria
